+# Local patch set
+
+This directory documents the changes carried on top of the upstream project.
+It is intended to make future upstream updates easier to port.
+
+## Contents
+
+- `0001-postgres-and-dockerhub.diff` — unified diff against the original upstream snapshot used for this change set.
+- `DELETE_FILES.txt` — files removed as part of the PostgreSQL refactor.
+- `PORTING_NOTES.md` — structure and merge notes for future updates.
